<div class="allianceSection collapsable collapsed">
	 <h4 class="header">Fire Characteristics</h4>
	<div class="text">Stands have low density and sparse litter, usually lacking the fuel to carry a fire (Brooks and Minnich 2006). Most fires are infrequent and lighting caused, and affect individual trees. Surface fires are infrequent, slow burning, and of low intensity (Ahlenslager 1987). Stand dynamics are influenced more by climate and seed dispersal patterns than by fire (Howard 2004b).</div>
	<table class="zebraStripe">
		
